Pre-Game Insights: Achraf Hakimi is expected to be a key player for Morocco, versatile in both attack and defense.
Themba Zwane is showing age is just a number and continues to be an integral part of South Africa's plan.
The winner will meet either Cape Verde or Mauritania in the quarter-finals.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Morocco national football team made a big name in the 2022 FIFA World Cup while finishing fourth.
South Africa played three group games but failed to open scoring in two of those games.
Bafana Bafana’s 4-0 win against Namibia is one of the two highest winning margins so far in the tournament.
The Confederation of African Football (CAF) lifted the ban on head coach Walid Regragui, it comes as a major boost for Morocco.
Hugo Broos’s men have no major issues in the squad right now.
Achraf Hakim Ziyech, was subbed off with an ankle injury and remains a doubt.
Morocco made it to the Round of 16 after finishing as Group F winner while South Africa came second in Group E
